# python program to check wheather the person is eligible to vote or not

age=int(input("Enter the age of a person:"))
if age>=18:
    print("Person eligible to vote")
else:
    print("Person is not eligible to vote he needs ",18-age," more years to vote")

output:
Enter the age of a person:3
Person is not eligible to vote he needs  15  more years to vote
